    "body" : "<p>In Mac: </p>\n\n<p><strong>Kill process</strong>\nTerminal: <code>kill &lt;pid&gt;</code></p>\n\n<p><strong>Find pid:</strong>\nTerminal: <code>lsof -i:&lt;port&gt;</code></p>\n\n<p>From Diego Pino answer</p>\n"
  }, {
