    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>In windows </p>\n\n<pre><code>netstat -ano\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>will list all the protocols, ports and processes listening .\nUse</p>\n\n<pre><code>taskkill -pid \"proces to kill\" /f\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>to kill the process listening to the port.\ne.g</p>\n\n<pre><code> taskkill -pid 431 /f\n</code></pre>\n"
  }, {
    "owner" : {
      "account_id" : 1835870,
      "reputation" : 128,
      "user_id" : 1666285,
      "user_type" : "registered",
      "profile_image" : "https://www.gravatar.com/avatar/d8a7f31be93810e7f821c3e6f40c73e5?s=256&d=identicon&r=PG",
