    "creation_date" : 1439799300,
    "answer_id" : 32045608,
    "question_id" : 12737293,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>In Windows CMD line, find out the Process ID that hold a connection on the bind port by entering following command:</p>\n\n<p>C:> netstat -a -o</p>\n\n<p>-a show all connections</p>\n\n<p>-o show process identifier</p>\n\n<p>And then <strong>Terminate</strong> the process.</p>\n"
  }, {
