    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>Restart the PC once, I think it will work. It started working in my case. One more thing can be done go to Task Manager and End the process. </p>\n\n<p><a href=\"https://i.sstatic.net/5nity.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\"><img src=\"https://i.sstatic.net/5nity.png\" alt=\"Screenshot for the reference.\"></a></p>\n"
